Privacy Policy for XPOphi

Last Updated: April 8, 2025

We respect your privacy and aim to be transparent about what data XPOphi collects and how it is used.

1. Data Collected

User IDs and Server IDs (to track XP and levels).

Message Counts (but not actual message content).

No personally identifiable information (PII) is stored.


2. How Data is Used

To provide leveling and engagement features.

To track user progression within servers.


3. Data Storage & Retention

Data is stored securely and is not shared with third parties.

Inactive server data may be purged after 60 days.


4. User Rights

You may request data removal by contacting the bot owner.


5. Changes to the Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated. Changes will be reflected on this page.

